Package sample.Model

Class Donut

java.lang.Object
sample.Model.MenuItem
sample.Model.Donut
public class Donut
extends MenuItem
The Donut class handles all operations relating to manipulating donuts, including setting the donut's flavor, changing its quantity, and calculating its price.
